QuestData.Title: Back to Brennadam
QuestData.Description:
The naga are mostly cleared out thanks to your help. They'll think twice before attacking again.
Can you return to Brennadam and tell Squire Augustus III to return to his normal station?
QuestData.LogDescription: Report back to Squire Augustus III at Brennadam.
QuestData.RewardText: Oh, roger! I'll head back at once!
